---
title: Sriracha-Glazed BBQ Pork Rissoles with Roast Veggie Toss & Herby Yoghurt
description: Roll up your sleeves and get stuck into making tonight’s sriracha-glazed juicy rissoles. Combine them with our
barbecue seasoning and a bit of garlic, cook and eat (that’s the best part!), it’s that easy. Add a colourful array of roast
veggies, then cool your taste buds with a herby yoghurt to finish the dish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

